1. Include 5-8 main H2 sections
2. Each H2 should have 2-3 H3 subsections
3. Address all search intents from analysis
4. Cover competitor content gaps
5. Natural keyword usage (avoid stuffing)
6. Structure for featured snippet optimization

Return ONLY the JSON, no explanations or markdown.
